data.description: Motivated sellers! All brick/vinyl siding 3 bedroom 2 bath home! Entire house has  engineered hardwood flooring installed in 2022!  Interior freshly painted in 2022! Kitchen features tons of cabinet and countertop space featuring a large island offering plenty of seating! Breakfast room and formal dining room. Salon bath with jacuzzi tub and sep shower!Some plantation blinds!  Lots of updated light fixtures! Front/rear security doors. Ring doorbell/flood light Seller is related to listing agent.
